  <div class="modal-content">
    <div class="modal-title">
      ğŸ’¬ å¼•ç”¨ã‚’è¿½åŠ 
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal()">Ã—</button>
    </div>

    <div id="modalBody">
      <div class="loading-state" id="loadingState">
        <div class="loading-spinner"></div>
        <div>AIãŒåè¨€ã‚’æ¢ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™...</div>
      </div>

