        <p id="errorMessage">ã‚¨ãƒ©ãƒ¼ãŒç™ºç”Ÿã—ã¾ã—ãŸ</p>
        <button class="btn-submit" onclick="loadSuggestions()" style="margin-top: 15px;">å†è©¦è¡Œ</button>
